### =====================================================
### Read back – score is auto-computed after the 13th
### sample upload; fetch latest persisted result here
### =====================================================

### 31. Get latest computed score
GET {{baseUrl}}/stress/scores/latest
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}

### =====================================================
### Error paths
### =====================================================

### 32. No auth on latest score → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/stress/scores/latest

